        <p class="lead">HVAC dispatch is the command center of your operation. The difference between companies booking $800K annually versus $2M often comes down to how efficiently they run their dispatch board. After analyzing operations at 200+ HVAC companies, here are the proven systems that separate the leaders from the laggards.</p>

        <p>The best dispatchers increase revenue per truck by 35-50% while reducing customer complaints by 60%. They achieve this through systematic priority rules, intelligent routing, and constant optimization of technician schedules.</p>

        <h2 id="priority-matrix">Setting Up Your Priority Matrix</h2>

        <p>Every call that comes into your dispatch board needs immediate classification. Top HVAC companies use a 4-tier priority system that eliminates guesswork and reduces average response times by 40%.</p>

        <div style="overflow-x: auto; margin: 2rem 0;">
          <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; border: 1px solid #ddd;">
