              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Urgent (P2)</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">2-4 hours</td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Complete system failure, commercial down</td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">25-40% upcharge</td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="background: #f8f9fa;">
                <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Same Day (P3)</strong></td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">4-8 hours</td>
                <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Partial cooling loss, strange noises</td>
